      {"@type":"Question","name":"Can I check my electricity bill by SMS without internet?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. All major DISCOs (LESCO, IESCO, FESCO, GEPCO, MEPCO, PESCO, HESCO, SEPCO, QESCO, TESCO) offer SMS bill inquiry. Send your 14-digit reference number to the DISCO's SMS short code. Works on any phone with SMS capability — no internet needed."}},
